<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>通用汽车或剥离电动汽车业务，股价随后飙升至三个月以来最高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/35f1e92bb4a740cab0b643161b5599db.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
